// ==================== ŸÖŸÉŸàŸÜ ÿßŸÑÿ™ÿ£ÿ¨Ÿäÿ±ÿßÿ™ ÿßŸÑŸÜÿ¥ÿ∑ÿ© ====================
const ActiveRentals = ({ rentals, onAction, loading }) => {
  const [countdowns, setCountdowns] = useState({});

  useEffect(() => {
    const updateCountdowns = () => {
      const newCountdowns = {};
      
      rentals.forEach(rental => {
        if (!rental) return;
        
        const isOpenTime = rental.is_open_time || rental.rental_type === 'open';
        
        if (!isOpenTime) {
          const endTime = new Date(rental.start_time);
          endTime.setMinutes(endTime.getMinutes() + (rental.duration_minutes || 0));
          const now = new Date();
          
          if (now > endTime) {
            newCountdowns[rental.id] = { text: '‚è∞ ÿßŸÜÿ™ŸáŸâ', expired: true };
          } else {
            const diffMs = endTime - now;
            const minutes = Math.floor(diffMs / 60000);
            const seconds = Math.floor((diffMs % 60000) / 1000);
            newCountdowns[rental.id] = { 
              text: `${minutes}:${seconds.toString().padStart(2, '0')}`,
              warning: minutes < 5 
            };
          }
        } else {
          const startTime = new Date(rental.start_time);
          const now = new Date();
          const diffMs = now - startTime;
          const minutes = Math.floor(diffMs / 60000);
          const seconds = Math.floor((diffMs % 60000) / 1000);
          newCountdowns[rental.id] = { 
            text: `‚è≥ ${minutes}:${seconds.toString().padStart(2, '0')}` 
          };
        }
      });
      
      setCountdowns(newCountdowns);
    };

    updateCountdowns();
    const interval = setInterval(updateCountdowns, 1000);
    
    return () => clearInterval(interval);
  }, [rentals]);

  if (loading) {
    return (
      <div className="active-rentals-section">
        <div className="loading-state">
          <Loader2 className="spinner" size={32} />
          <p>ÿ¨ÿßÿ±Ÿä ÿ™ÿ≠ŸÖŸäŸÑ ÿßŸÑÿ™ÿ£ÿ¨Ÿäÿ±ÿßÿ™ ÿßŸÑŸÜÿ¥ÿ∑ÿ©...</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    );
  }

  if (rentals.length === 0) {
    return (
      <div className="active-rentals-section">
        <div className="section-header">
          <div className="section-title">
            <Zap size={24} />
            <div>
              <h3>ÿßŸÑÿ™ÿ£ÿ¨Ÿäÿ±ÿßÿ™ ÿßŸÑŸÜÿ¥ÿ∑ÿ©</h3>
              <p className="section-subtitle">ŸÑÿß ÿ™Ÿàÿ¨ÿØ ÿ™ÿ£ÿ¨Ÿäÿ±ÿßÿ™ ŸÜÿ¥ÿ∑ÿ© ÿ≠ÿßŸÑŸäÿßŸã</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div className="empty-state">
          <Clock size={48} />
          <h3>ŸÑÿß ÿ™Ÿàÿ¨ÿØ ÿ™ÿ£ÿ¨Ÿäÿ±ÿßÿ™ ŸÜÿ¥ÿ∑ÿ©</h3>
          <p>ÿßÿ®ÿØÿ£ ÿ™ÿ£ÿ¨Ÿäÿ± ÿ¨ÿØŸäÿØ ŸÖŸÜ ŸÇÿßÿ¶ŸÖÿ© ÿßŸÑÿ£ŸÑÿπÿßÿ®</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    );
  }

  return (
    <div className="active-rentals-section">
      <div className="section-header">
        <div className="section-title">
          <Zap size={24} />
          <div>
            <h3>ÿßŸÑÿ™ÿ£ÿ¨Ÿäÿ±ÿßÿ™ ÿßŸÑŸÜÿ¥ÿ∑ÿ©</h3>
            <p className="section-subtitle">
              {rentals.length} ÿ™ÿ£ÿ¨Ÿäÿ± ŸÜÿ¥ÿ∑ ÿ≠ÿßŸÑŸäÿßŸã
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div className="rentals-grid">
        {rentals.map(rental => {
          const countdown = countdowns[rental.id] || { text: '--:--' };
          const isOpenTime = rental.is_open_time || rental.rental_type === 'open';
          
          return (
            <div key={rental.id} className="rental-card">
              <div className="rental-header">
                <div className="rental-number">
                  <strong>#{rental.rental_number || rental.id}</strong>
                  {isOpenTime && <span className="badge open">ŸÖŸÅÿ™Ÿàÿ≠</span>}
                </div>
                <div className="rental-time">
                  <Clock size={14} />
                  <span className={countdown.warning ? 'warning' : ''}>
                    {countdown.text}
                  </span>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div className="rental-body">
                <div className="customer-info">
                  <h4>{rental.customer_name}</h4>
                  <p>{rental.customer_phone}</p>
                </div>
                
                <div className="game-info">
                  <p>{rental.game_name}</p>
                  <span className="rental-amount">
                    {formatCurrency(rental.total_amount || 0)}
                  </span>
                </div>
                
                <div className="payment-status">
                  <span className={`status-badge ${rental.payment_status === 'ŸÖÿØŸÅŸàÿπ' ? 'paid' : 'pending'}`}>
                    {rental.payment_status === 'ŸÖÿØŸÅŸàÿπ' ? '‚úÖ ŸÖÿØŸÅŸàÿπ' : '‚è≥ ' + rental.payment_status}
                  </span>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div className="rental-actions">
                <button
                  onClick={() => onAction('details', rental)}
                  className="btn-action view"
                  title="ÿπÿ±ÿ∂ ÿßŸÑÿ™ŸÅÿßÿµŸäŸÑ"
                >
                  <Eye size={16} />
                </button>
                
                {isOpenTime && (
                  <button
                    onClick={() => onAction('end', rental)}
                    className="btn-action end"
                    title="ÿ•ŸÜŸáÿßÿ° ÿßŸÑŸàŸÇÿ™"
                  >
                    <Clock size={16} />
                  </button>
                )}
                
                <button
                  onClick={() => onAction('cancel', rental)}
                  className="btn-action cancel"
                  title="ÿ•ŸÑÿ∫ÿßÿ° ÿßŸÑÿ™ÿ£ÿ¨Ÿäÿ±"
                >
                  <XCircle size={16} />
                </button>
              </div>
            </div>
          );
        })}
      </div>
    </div>
  );
};

